{{Cleanup|date=August 2007}}

The '''Multi-Purpose Viewer''' is an [[open-source software]], [[cross-platform]] image generator (IG) that implements the [[Common Image Generator Interface]], the standard way for a host device to communicate with an image generator (IG) in the simulation industry.

